        "translation": "They must all invite the saṃgha to wholeheartedly seek liberation.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b19_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不疑不昧。",
        "translation": "They must not doubt or be obscured.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b19_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "信心清淨。",
        "translation": "Their faith and mind are purified.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b20_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "然後可屈。",
        "translation": "Then they can submit.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b20_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "近世有一長者聞說賓頭盧阿羅漢受佛教勅為末法人作福田。",
        "translation": "In a recent life, there was an elder who heard that the Piṇḍola arhat had been commanded by Buddhism to work as a field of merit for those of the last generation.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b20_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "即如法施設大會。",
        "translation": "He immediately set up a large assembly according to the teaching.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b22_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "至心請賓頭盧。",
        "translation": "He wholeheartedly invited Piṇḍola.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b22_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "氍氀下遍布華。",
        "translation": "Flowers were spread all over the bottom of the woolly bedding.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b22_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "欲以驗之。",
        "translation": "He wanted to test it.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b23_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大眾食訖。",
