        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b23_10",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "發氍氀華皆萎。",
        "translation": "They found that the woolly flowers had all withered.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b23_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "懊惱自責。",
        "translation": "They were distressed and criticized themselves.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b24_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不知過所從來。",
        "translation": "They didn't know where the mistake had come from.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b24_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "更復精竭。",
        "translation": "They then exerted themselves even more.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b24_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "審問經師。",
        "translation": "He asked the sūtras about it.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b25_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "重設大會。",
        "translation": "He resumed the great assembly.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b25_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如前華亦復皆萎。",
        "translation": "Like the previous one, the flowers also withered.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b25_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復更傾竭盡家財產。",
        "translation": "He then poured out all of his family's possessions.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b25_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復作大會。",
        "translation": "He then reconstructed the great assembly.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b26_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "猶亦如前。",
        "translation": "It would still be like the previous one.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b26_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "懊惱自責。",
        "translation": "He was so distressed that he blamed himself.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b26_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "更請百餘法師。",
        "translation": "He invited a hundred other teachers of the Dharma.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b27_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "求請所失。",
        "translation": "He asked them to request what had been lost.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b27_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "懺謝罪過。",
        "translation": "He asked them to repent of their faults.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b27_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如向上座一人年老。",
        "translation": "Suppose he were to ascend to the throne, where one person was elderly.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b28_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "四布悔其愆咎。",
        "translation": "He repented of his transgressions in four different ways.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b28_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上座告之。",
        "translation": "The superior monk told him.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b28_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝三會請我。",
        "translation": "\"You've invited me three times.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b29_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我皆受請。",
        "translation": "I accepted all of your invitations.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b29_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "汝自使奴門中見遮。",
