        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784b29_5",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "以我年老衣服弊壞。",
        "translation": "It's because I'm old and my clothes are tattered.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c01_6",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "謂是被擯。",
        "translation": "You say you've been rejected.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c01_7",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賴提沙門不肯見前。",
        "translation": "The ratiṣṭacāritra monk refused to see me.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c01_8",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我以汝請欲強入。",
        "translation": "I wanted to force you to come in because you asked me to.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c02_9",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
