        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c03_11",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是第二會亦來。",
        "translation": "This second meeting also came.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c03_12",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復不見前。",
        "translation": "Again, he didn't see the front.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c03_13",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "我又欲強入。",
        "translation": "I wanted to force my way in again.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c04_14",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復打我頭額中瘡。",
