        "translation": "He got a sore on the left corner of his forehead.",
        "source": "T32n1689_001:0784c05_18",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是皆汝自為之。",
        "translation": "You did this all by yourself.",
